  "description": "This STAC extension provides comprehensive fields for documenting liability information and claims associated with geospatial data. It is designed to track incidents, damages, legal proceedings, insurance information, and data quality/provenance related to spatial data assets.\n\nKey features:\n- **Liability Claims Management**: Track claim status, types, jurisdictions, damages, and affected parties\n- **ISO 19115/19115-4 Quality**: Full support for completeness, accuracy, lineage, and imagery quality\n- **DGIWG Compliance**: Defence geospatial quality elements\n- **W3C PROV Provenance**: Complete PROV-JSON support for semantic web integration\n- **Legal/Insurance**: Policy numbers, providers, evidence references, resolution tracking\n- **Semantic Web**: JSON-LD context with Schema.org, FIBO, DQV, and PROV mappings",
